<resolution-body style="traditional" id="H6431435E80294B1FB0CE0F8AD3CEE975"> 
<section display-inline="yes-display-inline" section-type="undesignated-section" id="HBC74D2FB82C7492AA6454AB7A7A519DF"><text>That the following named Members be, and are hereby, elected to the following standing committees of the House of Representatives:</text> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Natural Resources:</header><text>Ms. Conway.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Veterans’ Affairs:</header><text>Ms. Conway.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Agriculture:</header><text>Mrs. Flores.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Homeland Security:</header><text>Mrs. Flores.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on the Budget:</header><text>Mr. Moore of Utah, to rank immediately after Mr. Smith of Missouri. </text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

</section> 
